		  /// Returns the image data if found or Nil if not.
		  ///
		  /// Assumes `container.Characters(startPos) = "!"` and `container.Characters(startPos + 1) = "["`.
		  /// Assumes `container.Characters(closerCharPos)` is the index of a "]" character.
		  
